data.description: One of a kind, custom built, all brick home located in the gated community of Island View in Woodcreek Farms on .61 of an acre, 4 Bedrooms/4.5 Baths, 3328 SF all on ONE LEVEL with a 3 car garage AND on the Fairway of Hole #10 on the Golf Course!  Home includes 2 decorative/distinctive Electric Fireplaces; Custom built/designed coffered ceilings with built in recessed lighting; Custom designed lighting fixtures; A “WOW” Master Bath; All rooms have en-suite facilities; Chef’s Kitchen which has its own ZIP CODE; Home is SONOS wired throughout for data and TV's; AND SO MUCH MORE!  Perfect home for family/friends gathering or just to relax on your own! This is a must see!  Call for a showing.
